                </p>
                <p>
                  In the second graph, not everyone gets sick in the outbreak. The <m>S(t)</m> curve appears to level out at a value of approximately <m>8</m>. Extending <c>t_range</c> beyond <m>t=20</m> can help for confirming this.
                </p>
