              <p>
                This model has more pieces than the models we have seen before. It may take some time to think through these pieces! <em>Begin by taking a significant amount of time to view the compartmental diagram in <xref ref="fig-SIA-compartmental-diagram"/> and read the ideas that led to the model's development. Be sure you understand them.</em> Then respond to the following questions.
              </p>

